-- Bwin.Party CEO Says It’s ‘When, not If’ U.S. Online Poker Opens
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2012-03-29T07:47:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-29/bwin-party-ceo-says-it-s-when-not-if-u-s-online-poker-opens.html
Bwin.Party Digital Entertainment
Plc (BPTY)  co-Chief Executive Officer Norbert Teufelberger said it is a
question of “when, not if” the U.S. online poker market opens
up and it would present a significant opportunity for the
company.  “It is a significant opportunity for the company because
in our history, we had 50 percent market share, that market was
close to three quarters of a billion dollars,” to the company,
Teufelberger said in a conference call today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
